- **Symbol**: MFT
- **Price**: Real-time price based on Oracle data, initially set to 1 MFT = 1 USD.


### **Conclusion
Flash Token (MFT) is an innovative step in decentralized finance, leveraging the power of flash loans and real-time pricing through an oracle. With its focus on fast and secure loans, MFT is set to empower users with greater flexibility and opportunities in the DeFi space.
         

